\v 2 Kodwa iguma\x + Hez. 40.17.20.\x*\x + Mat. 26.3.\x* elingaphandle kwethempeli ulitshiye ngaphandle, futhi ungalilinganisi; ngoba linikelwe ezizweni\x + Luka 21.24. Dan. 8.13. Hlab. 79.1.\x*; njalo zizanyathelela phansi umuzi ongcwele\x + 21.2; 22.19. Neh. 11.1.\x*\x + Luka 21.24 Dan. 8.13. Hlab. 79.1.\x* inyanga ezingamatshumi amane lambili\x + 13.5. 11.3. 12.6. 12.14.\x*.
