\v 5 Uba kukhona othanda ukubalimaza, umlilo uphuma emlonyeni wabo\x + 2 Kho. 1.10,12. Jer. 5.14.\x*, uqothule izitha zabo; njalo uba umuntu efisa ukubalimaza, ngokunjalo kumele abulawe\x + Nani 16.35.\x*.
