\v 18 Lezizwe sezithukuthele, lolaka lwakho selufikile\x + Hlab. 110.5.\x*, lesikhathi sabafileyo\x + Isam. 20.12. Dan. 7.10. Isam. 14.7; 20.4. 6.10.\x* ukuthi bahlulelwe, lesokunika umvuzo ezincekwini zakho abaprofethi labangcwele\x + 16.6.\x* labesaba ibizo lakho\x + 19.5.\x*, abancinyane labakhulu\x + 19.5.\x*\x + Seb. 26.22.\x*, lesokubhubhisa ababhubhisa\f + \fk ukubhubhisa: \fl kumbe, \fq ukonakalisa.\f* umhlaba.
